UID:2602118bZs3U-rYEiw3Q6GRPxnIw
DESCRIPTION:**Celebrate Women With Vision for Women's History Month**\n\n
 Women’s stories want to be told. It's Women's History Month. Let’s l
 ift the voices of women with vision from cultures across the world and cel
 ebrate them through story and poetry with readings from local authors Anna
  Citrino\, Jean Gordon Kocienda\, and Pamela Reitman. \n\nStories hold t
 he world together and help us see ourselves in others' lives. Come share 
 a meal and listen to a few stories of some amazing women.\n\n**To RSVP (Re
 quired) see: https://aqus.com/communitydinnerRSVP/**\n\n*To learn more ab
 out Aqus Cafe Community Dinners\, see:* ***https://aqus.com/communitydinne
 rs/***
