BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Forró Dance with Eric and Abigail
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260326T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260326T203000
UID:260319n6l7acP0aEattmwiUDG0zA
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to connect\, spin\, and glide to the irresistible rh
 ythms of Forró! Originating in the Northeast of Brazil\, Forró is a cap
 tivating partner dance known for its close embrace\, playful steps\, and i
 nfectious\, feel-good music. It is a social dance that will enrich your li
 fe\, perfect for a night out or a casual gathering.\n\nYou Will Learn:\n\n
 The Basic Step & Close Embrace: You will master the foundational quick-qui
 ck-slow rhythm and learn how to comfortably and confidently navigate the e
 ssential close-hold connection that defines Forró.\n\nLeading & Following
  Techniques: Discover the clear\, subtle body cues required to effortlessl
 y lead your partner through turns and variations\, and how to follow with 
 grace and responsiveness.\n\nTraveling & Stationary Patterns: Learn fundam
 ental steps like the ‘Caminhada’ \\(walking step\\) and common station
 ary turns that will allow you to dance on any size floor.\n\nRhythm & Musi
 cality: Connect your movement to the distinct musical styles of Forró—f
 rom the mellow ‘Xote’ to the faster\, more energetic ‘Pé-de-Serra.
 ’\n\nThis class is perfect for anyone looking to learn a social partner 
 dance\, connect with Brazilian culture\, and enjoy a vibrant\, community a
 tmosphere. No partner or prior dance experience is required! Just bring yo
 ur enthusiasm and comfortable shoes!\n\nClass Details\n\nNote: Arrive 10 
 minutes before. No floor marking shoe soles allowed.\n\nDate & Time: Thur
 sdays @7:30PM – 8:30PM\n\nAddress: 4140 Redwood Highway \\#8 San Rafael
 \, CA
LOCATION:4140 Redwood Highway #8
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/forr-dance-with-eric-an
 d-abigail/17624419/2026-03-26T19
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Brandlin Estate Wine & Food Tasting Experience
