 y CTE Foundation and North Coast Builders Exchange\, an evening designed f
 or meaningful connection\, conversation\, and community. Enjoy relationshi
 p-building in a casual setting as you reconnect with fellow Chamber member
 s\, meet new business contacts\, and engage with guests from across Sonoma
  County. This mixer brings together two organizations deeply committed to 
 supporting students and strengthening our region’s future workforce. Lea
 rn more about how education\, industry\, and community partners are collab
 orating to create real pathways and opportunities for local youth. Come ex
 change ideas\, expand your network\, and get inspired by the collective im
 pact happening right here in our county. Please RSVP in advance. Complimen
 tary for Chamber Members / $35 for Non-Members.
