DESCRIPTION:Join WALT Wines at  Sonoma Epicurean's Epic Party \, a high-en
 ergy kickoff celebration at Bacchus Landing. Part of the signature Sonoma 
 Epicurean series\, the weekend showcases curated\, hands-on experiences wi
 th award-winning chefs\, local artisans\, and world-class vintners. The Ep
 ic Party sets the tone with a lively\, welcoming atmosphere where guests c
 an circulate freely\, tasting exceptional wines and savoring culinary bite
 s from Sonoma's talented chefs and producers. It's a relaxed\, social even
 ing designed for connection\, discovery\, and celebration-bringing togethe
 r an engaged\, wine-loving audience in one vibrant setting. Proceeds from 
 Sonoma Epicurean support the V Foundation for Cancer Research\, helping fu
 nd groundbreaking cancer research and related programs.
