BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Cumbia with Mireille
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260327T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260327T203000
UID:2603244KrYURO48UOTZR1bq7kanw
DESCRIPTION:Feel the Rhythm with Cumbia\n\nReady to master the “Step of 
 the Soul”? Join us for a high-energy cumbia class where we dive into the
  heart of Latin America’s most infectious dance. Whether you have two le
 ft feet or you’re a dance floor regular\, this class will get you moving
  with confidence.\n\nMireille will guide you through:\n\nBasic directional
  steps: The signature back-break basic step\, essential turns\, and the 
 “Guacharaca” rhythm.\n\nThe Vibe: No partner required\, no experience
  necessary—just bring your energy and a pair of comfortable shoes!\n\nIm
 portant Details\n\nNo dance experience required: Whether you’ve never d
 anced before or it’s been a while\, you’re welcome here!\n\nNo partner
  necessary: Come solo or bring a friend—either way\, you’ll have plen
 ty of opportunities to dance.\n\nPlease wear non-marking shoe soles: Thi
 s helps us keep our dance floor in great condition.\n\nCome join us and di
 scover the joy of cumbia. We can’t wait to see you on the dance floor.\n
 \nDate & Time: every 4th Fridays\, 7:30pm\n\nInstructor: Mireille Ruiz 
 Born and raised in Mexico City\, she grew up dancing and listening to Lati
 n Music as part of her culture including Cumbia\, Banda\, ranchera\, quebr
 adita\, etc. she learned her first following Techniques\, dancing with her
  father in every family fiesta. she has a background in Mexican folklore\,
  Jazz\, tap dancing and gymnastics\, she also is a percussionist\, drummer
  and Montessori Teacher.\n\nShe grew up performing since she the age of 4.
  Bay Area bachata and cumbia dance instructor\, Mireille has been teaching
  dance\, performing\,  leading dance teams\, around USA events\, dance f
 estivals\, congresses since 2008\n\nAddress: 4140 Redwood Highway \\#8 San
  Rafael\, CA\n\nNote: Arrive 10 minutes before. No floor marking shoe sole
 s allowed.
LOCATION:Salsa Dance Marin
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/cumbia-with-mireille/18
 336616/2026-03-27T19
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Intermediate Salsa with Tyler
