DESCRIPTION:The American Canyon Arts Foundation is hosting an Irish Cultur
 al Event on Friday\, March 28\, starting at 6pm. It will be held in our Ro
 om 5 of the Napa Junction Community Center. This free event is funded in p
 art with a grant from the Napa County Arts & Culture Commission.\n\nWe wil
 l start with a simple Irish meal\, accompanied with Irish music from local
  musician\, Rich Adams. When we’re done eating\, we’ll watch a documen
 tary\, entitled “Hidden Ireland.” This film highlights Irish geography
 \, culture and history.\n\nSpace is limited\, so you need to RSVP to get y
 our ticket. The dinner and event is free\, but we plan to have beer and wi
 ne available for sale.\n\nAnd\, of course\, if you want to help out financ
 ially\, that’s appreciated\, too! We hope this format is successful\, si
 nce it will let us produce more cultural awareness programs at an affordab
 le price.
