DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260328T130000
UID:260319dHD2LEO6m0m336ele6BuBg
DESCRIPTION:Birds do it all for love: singing\, dancing\, offering food\, 
 building nests\, and scouting the landscape for the perfect place to raise
  their young. As early spring arrives\, many of our native birds are not o
 nly beginning courtship rituals but also actively exploring territories an
 d nesting sites.  \n\nJoin us as we take a closer look at the nesting act
 ivity that may be unfolding right in your own backyard. Meet our Ambassado
 r birds\, examine sample nests up close\, and learn about our work\, our r
 enesting program\, and how you can play a role in protecting critical nest
 ing habitats during this busy season.
LOCATION:The Bird Rescue Center
URL:https://www.birdrescuecenter.org/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
