DESCRIPTION:***Join us*** for **NO KINGS Napa** on March 28 from 1-2:30pm
  at Oxbow Commons for a lively\, short rally with speakers\, drumming\, an
 d music\, then a march through downtown Napa.\n\n **Let's make this the la
 rgest one-day mass rally in American history and** peacefully and joyfully
  demonstrate our love of country\, our support for our immigrant communiti
 es\, our embrace of love over hate\, and respect for the rule of law and o
 ur Constitution!\n\nLet's send the message to this administration and say 
