 work by two accomplished Sonoma artists who distill the essence of the nat
 ural world through bold and semi-abstract interpretations of trees\, liche
 ns\, birds' nests\, and more. The exhibition is a deep immersion into the 
 energies and strategies of the natural world. Exhibition opening reception
  March 21\, 5-7 pm. Free and open to the public. Come celebrate the beauty
  of spring in Sonoma with us!
LOCATION:Alley Gallery
