 enter for the Arts\n\nSonoma Botanical Garden\n\nSonoma Valley Museum of A
 rt\n\n\\*Must visit with a child to receive entry to the Children’s Muse
 um of Sonoma County.\n\nNot a member? Join any of the participating museum
 s to enjoy the weeklong reciprocal benefit! The Schulz Museum will offer 
 door prizes for new Members who sign up in person at the Museum on the SWA
 P Week kick-off date\, Saturday\, March 28 \\(memberships start at $50 an
 d include special events\, discounts\, exclusive collectibles\, and more\\
