 ave Center plus our focused intentions\, for Peace in our communities\, ou
 rselves and our world. It’s a valuable window to help change course for 
 the better. More prayer now to strengthen possibilities for peace! This ev
 ent is a powerful Peace prayer and crystal bowl sound healing\, we hope yo
 u can join us!”\n\nThings have changed since we first started OM Peace p
 rayers\, with Peace between India and Pakistan plus 5 other conflicts. We
 ’d like to see an end to the Ukraine-Russia conflict\, and continued Pea
 ce in the middle east. It’s all happening in this very moment.\n\nIn the
  2nd hour we direct the potent field created in the first through suggeste
 d visioning\, sharing dialog and a sound bath to help us all integrate. Co
 me join OM for Peace and lets Be The Change We Want to See in the World!\n
 \nAbout Your Guides\n\nEmile Canning is a Mediator & former owner of The 
 Integratron. He is a pioneer in frequency healing and personal growth. Pro
 ducer of Peacewave Productions\, creator of uplifting & peaceful events th
 roughout California.\n\nAnanda Fierro is an Advanced Bodyworker & Sound-E
 nergy Healer\, utilizing unique frequency medical devices to accelerate po
 sitive outcomes\, for over 2 decades. She studied with Jill Purce\, Sound 
 & Ancestral Healing pioneer in the UK.
