BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Marjorie Prime
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260329T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260329T152000
UID:250801j4feTGpTUU-ZRmgbsfYP3Q
DESCRIPTION:**Artificial Remembrance: The Intersection of Technology and M
 emory**\n\n***“Jordan Harrison’s gently uncanny play imagines a future
  solution for a person in mourning: the recreation of someone you love as 
 an artificial intelligence.”* —Kate Wyver\, The Guardian**\n\n**In *Ma
 rjorie Prime*\, playwright Jordan Harrison delves into the intricate dance
  between human memory and artificial intelligence. Set in the not-so-dista
 nt future\, the narrative centers on 85-year-old Marjorie\, whose mind is 
 gradually succumbing to dementia. To combat her fading recollections\, her
  family introduces her to a “Prime”—a lifelike holographic projectio
 n of her late husband\, Walter\, programmed to retell the stories of their
  shared past. As Marjorie interacts with Walter Prime\, the lines between 
 authentic memories and reconstructed narratives blur\, prompting profound 
 questions about identity\, the reliability of our recollections\, and the 
 extent to which technology can replicate the essence of human connection. 
 This thought-provoking drama challenges audiences to consider what we choo
 se to remember\, what we wish to forget\, and how the digital age reshapes
  the very fabric of our personal histories.**\n\n***Marjorie Prime* has ga
 rnered critical acclaim for its insightful exploration and profound commen
 tary on the human condition in an era where technology increasingly intert
 wines with our daily lives.**\n\nThursdays\, Fridays & Saturdays @ 7:30pm\
 , Saturdays and Sundays at 2:00pm Run Time: One hour\, 20 mins including i
 ntermission\n\nThursdays Adult $33 Fri/Sat Eve Adult $39.95\; Senior $36.9
 5\; Under 18 $26.95 Sat/Sun Matinee Adult $47.95\; Senior $44.95 \\*All pr
 ices include fees (707) 523-4185 **boxoffice@6thstreetplayhouse.com**
LOCATION:6th Street Playhouse
URL:https://6thstreetplayhouse.com/shows/2025-26/marjorie-prime/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
