DESCRIPTION:Celebrate community and get connected at the Sonoma County Vol
 unteer Fair.\n\nThis free community event brings together dozens of local 
 nonprofits\, public agencies\, and community groups looking for volunteers
 \, board members\, and supporters. Whether you're looking for a one-time o
 pportunity or a long-term way to give back\, the Volunteer Fair makes it e
 asy to find a cause that aligns with your interests and skills.\n\nIn hono
 r of César Chávez Day and National Volunteer Month\, attendees can also 
 participate in an on-site service project supporting **The Botanical Bus**
 \, a bilingual mobile clinic providing culturally centered healthcare for 
 Latine and Indigenous immigrant communities.\n\nStop by anytime during the
  event to:\n\n~Meet local nonprofits and community organizations\n\n~Learn
  about volunteer opportunities across Sonoma County\n\n~Participate in ass
 embling care bags for the Botanical Bus mobile clinic\n\n~Contribute to a 
 community art project honoring César Chávez Day\n\n~Connect with neighbo
 rs who care about strengthening our community\n\nEveryone is welcome — i
 ndividuals\, families\, students\, and anyone interested in making a diffe
 rence.
LOCATION:The Backdrop
URL:https://cvnl.org/sonoma-county-volunteer-fair/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
