DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260401T200000
UID:2603257L9xb1kWOkqsC_iRemMVEA
DESCRIPTION:You’ve probably heard about the Last Supper that Jesus share
 d with His disciples. It was actually a Passover meal. Or maybe you’ve s
 een the dramatic Passover scene in "The Ten Commandments" and wondered wha
 t the celebration is like. Come experience a meaningful Passover Seder wit
 h Hallel Fellowship! We’ll explore the ancient story of deliverance\, th
 e symbolic foods\, and how Jesus fills it all as our Passover Lamb. Join f
 riends for great food\, Scripture\, songs\, and reflection. Everyone welco
 me. No prior experience needed.
LOCATION:Jesus Cares 2020 Community Kitchen
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/passover-a-night-of-cel
 ebrating-freedom-in-the-messiah/18381000/2026-04-01T17
