DESCRIPTION:Join us for Stitch Café\, a cozy open studio held twice a mon
 th. Whether you're working on your own project or eager to explore new men
 ding techniques like darning and appliqué\, this is the perfect space to 
 gather\, share ideas\, and sew together. We provide hand-sewing supplies a
 nd materials\, but feel free to bring your own - it's all about community\
 , creativity\, and enjoying the process. By repairing what we already have
  and re-using materials\, we're not just preserving memories and adding un
 ique touches to our belongings - we’re also reducing waste and contribut
 ing to a more sustainable lifestyle. We can extend the life of our clothes
  and fabrics\, and take small but meaningful steps toward caring for the p
 lanet.
