BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Small Wonders
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T170000
UID:260324X6ibeDEF-kGPWGldvl4_7A
DESCRIPTION:Call for Art: Small Wonders\n\nSome of the most exquisite beau
 ty can be captured in the smallest of images and objects: the iridescence 
 of a hummingbird in flight\, a millefiori paperweight\, Faberge eggs\, or 
 a miniature woven basket. These pieces are modest in size but powerful in 
 creativity and expression.\n\nHealdsburg Center for the Arts (HCA) invites
  artists to submit paintings\, original fine art prints\, collage\, mixed 
 media\, drawings\, fiber arts\, sculptures\, ceramics\, and jewelry for th
 is exhibition.\n\nApplication Requirements:\n\n\\- Platform: All applicati
 ons must be submitted via EntryThingy\n\n\\- Eligibility: Work must be ori
 ginal and completed within the past two years. Photos in the application m
 ust represent the actual work intended for exhibition.\n\n\\- Size/Weight:
  Artwork must not exceed 12" x 12" unframed (144 sq in) or 196 sq in frame
 d. Maximum weight is 40 lbs.\n\n\\- Display: 2-D pieces must be securely w
 ired (no alligator clips). 3-D work must be stable\; artists are responsib
 le for on-site assembly if required.\n\n\\- Sales: All work must be for sa
 le. HCA retains a 40% commission\; artists receive 60%. Please list retail
  prices only.\n\nKey Dates:\n\n\\- Entry Deadline: May 10\, 2026 (9 PM)\n\
 n\\- Notification of Selection: By May 13\, 2026\n\n\\- Shipped Work Deadl
 ine: Wednesday\, May 27\, 2026 (must include pre-paid return label)\n\n\\-
  Hand-Delivery: Sunday\, May 31 (12–4 PM) and Monday\, June 1 (11 AM–1
  PM)\n\n\\- Exhibition Dates: June 4\, 2026 – July 19\, 2026\n\n\\- Open
 ing Reception: Saturday\, June 6\, 2026 (4–6 PM)\n\n\\- Pick-up/Return S
 hipping: July 19 (12–4 PM) and July 20 (11 AM–1 PM)\; shipping the wee
 k of July 20.\n\nEntry Fees:\n\n\\- Non-Members: $50 (1 entry)\, $55 (2 en
 tries)\, $60 (3 entries). Includes a $60 yearly supporter membership.\n\n\
 \- Current Members: $40 (1 entry)\, $45 (2 entries)\, $50 (3 entries).
LOCATION:Healdsburg Center for the Arts
URL:https://healdsburgcenterforthearts.org/small-wonders-2/
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Sourdough Supper Club
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T210000
UID:260324FnmFZhXh80WTzVcLTTUbQg
DESCRIPTION:Chicky & Dumplins\n\nApril 2\, 2026\, 6 to 9 pm\n\nJoin James 
 Beard Award-winning cookbook author Sarah Owens for a night of making lusc
 ious Chicken n' Dumplings with sourdough starter. If you've been looking f
 or ways to use your starter besides baking\, this is for you! Sarah will s
 how you how to make an unconventional roux and light and fluffy dumplings\
 , both with sourdough starter\, for a fun spin on this classic Southern co
 mfort food. To conclude the evening\, you will enjoy a sit-down meal of a 
 small appetizer\, chicken and dumplings\, salad\, and a light dessert. The
  chicken and dumplings include dairy and meat. One glass of locally produc
 ed wine or NA beverage is included. \n\nGalette Night\n\nApril 16\, 2026 
 6 to 9 pm\n\nJoin James Beard Award-winning cookbook author Sarah Owens fo
 r a night of galette making using a wholegrain sourdough pie crust. If you
 've been looking for ways to use your sourdough starter besides bread\, th
 is is for you! Sarah will show you how to roll out and fill a flaky\, whol
 esome pie crust made with spelt and sourdough starter\, perfect for both s
 weet and savory fillings. While the galettes are baking\, Sarah will demon
 strate how to mix the pie crust and provide you with a recipe to make at h
 ome. To conclude the evening\, you will enjoy a sit-down meal of soup\, a 
 savory galette\, salad\, and a light dessert. The soup and galette are veg
 etarian\, but both include dairy. One glass of locally produced wine or NA
  beverage is included.
LOCATION:Drewish Deli
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/sourdough-supper-club/1
 8370690/2026-04-02T18
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
