SUMMARY:Bottle Baby Breakfast Club
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T160000
UID:2603127EcBUeIZTkml7ZcUBHYQjQ
DESCRIPTION:**Tiny Hooves\, Big Hearts: Our Ongoing Rescue Mission**\n\n**
 At Goatlandia\, our mission is simple: to give love\, safety\, and a secon
 d chance to animals who need it most.**\n\n**We were recently called to re
 scue three baby goats. These tiny babies are now safe at Goatlandia\, and 
 they need bottle feeding several times a day to stay healthy and thrive.**
 \n\n**That’s Where You Come In: The Bottle Baby Breakfast Club**\n\n**St
 arting March 6th\, join us for a heartwarming hour on the farm\, bottle-fe
 eding and cuddling our newest rescues while supporting their care.**\n\n**
 Your $250 donation (covers milk and supplies for weeks of feedings) includ
 es admission for up to four guests for a private\, unforgettable visit to 
 Goatlandia.**\n\n**Come share the love\, feel the magic\, and help us give
  these little ones the future they deserve.**
LOCATION:Goatlandia
URL:https://www.goatlandia.org/bottle-babies-breakfast-club
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Imaginists present The Naturalists a new play by Jon Bernson
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T220000
UID:260309wIJbyhXiykGahv73_1FODQ
DESCRIPTION:The Imaginists present a new play by Jon Bernson about a reclu
 sive group of scientists whose radical discoveries challenge widely held a
 ssumptions about the world.The play unfolds across two interwoven timeline
 s: in the present\, the audience witnesses a sequence of high-stakes lectu
 res\, as each scientist unveils work that promises to reshape reality itse
 lf. Between these presentations\, the story flashes back to the week befor
 e the summit\, marked by the recent death of one of the Naturalists and es
 calating financial strain that threatens their fragile order.
LOCATION:The Imaginists
URL:https://theimaginists.org/the-naturalists-march-april
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
