 g/bookclubs 2026 Schedule February 5 - All the Colors of the Dark by Chris
  Whitaker March 5 - The Savage Kind by John Copenhaver April 2 - The House
  of Silk by Anthony Horowitz May 7 - The Midnight Feast by Lucy Foley June
  4 - Scorched Grace by Margot Douaihy July 2 - The Murders in Great Diddli
 ng by Katrina Bivald August 6 - The Antique Hunter's Guide to Murder by C.
 L. Miller September 3 - Daisy Darker by Alice Feeney October 1 - Three Bag
 s Full by Leonie Swann November 5 - How to Solve your own Murder by Kriste
