SUMMARY:Gas Money
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260403T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260403T200000
UID:260228iena6JePA0OHXwhCdzcDSg
DESCRIPTION:In the vibrant music scene of Sonoma County\, this young band 
 born right here in Windsor\, California is making waves with their electri
 fying performances and undeniable talent. Formed by four teenagers\, Gas M
 oney has quickly become a local favorite\, captivating audiences with thei
 r unique blend of alternative rock and infectious energy. Showing that roc
 k and roll isn’t dead\, they play all your favorite tunes\, ranging from
  Stevie Wonder to Metallica\, ensuring a musical journey you won't forget.
 \n\n**The Band Members:**\n\nCheyenne Vincent – Lead Vocals\n\nGavin Lee
  – Guitar and Vocals\n\nAlexander "AJ 18" Neujahr – Bass\n\nNick Caric
 o - Drums\n\nSince their humble beginnings in a living room in Windsor\, C
 A. Gas Money has been on a mission to bring quality musical performances t
 o every show. Their music blends elements of 80s\, 90s\, and 2000s rock\, 
 creating a nostalgic yet fresh experience for listeners of all ages. With 
 performances characterized by high energy\, tight musicianship\, and a gen
 uine love for music that shines through\, Gas Money creates a sound that r
 esonates with audiences and leaves them craving more!
LOCATION:Coyote Sonoma
URL:https://shop.coyotesonoma.com/gas-money-43-p217.aspx
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
