DESCRIPTION:Join author Monte Schulz as he talks about\, reads from\, an
 d signs his newest novel\, Undercity. Schulz has written several books\, 
 including Crossing Eden and Naughty\, and released the innovative album 
 Seraphonium. His latest book is a companion to his award-winning novel Me
 tropolis\, and dives deeper into the upside-down dystopian underground lab
 yrinth of cast-outs\, misanthropes\, and disenfranchised masses. Monte Sc
 hulz is the son of Peanuts creator and cartoonist Charles M. Schulz.
LOCATION:Charles M. Schulz Museum
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/monte-schulz-undercity/
