DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260404T213000
UID:260308SYGqGTRIm02vikCY4HlkcA
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma County’s bubbly burlesque dancer Velvet Thorn is back
  at the Mercury Theater with her company Epineux Productions for their yea
 rly fundraiser for Burlesque Hall of Fame! Help Velvet and friends fundrai
 se for the legends of burlesque\, the 20th century performers that paved t
 he way for burlesque as we know it today. And the theme of the evening? 00
 7 music! Mystery\, confidence\, sultriness\, and drama is the name of the 
 game for this evening of tease. \n\nWelcoming performers from near and fa
 r\, License To Tease will showcase the talent of today while honoring the 
 performers who shaped the world of burlesque. It’s the best of all world
 s when it comes to a fundraising event\, a highly entertaining evening tha
 t gives back in big ways to the folks we owe so much to\, the legends of b
 urlesque! \n\nCome and participate\, bring your dollars for the raffle an
 d your hollers for the performers\, and enjoy a night of dazzling burlesqu
 e (and more) at Petaluma’s premier historical theater. \n\nApril 4th\n\
 nDoors: 7:00 pm \n\nShow: 7:30 - 9:30 pm \n\nTickets: 25-45$ \n\nhttps:
 //app.arts-people.com/index.php?show=316142\n\nFor more information about 
 the legends of burlesque\, Burlesque Hall of Fame\, and Burlesque Hall of 
 Fame weekender visit https://burlesquehall.com/.\n\nFollow Epineux on Inst
 agram or Facebook @epineuxproductions or visit https://velvetthornburlesqu
 e.com/.
LOCATION:The Mercury Theater
URL:https://app.arts-people.com/index.php?show=316142
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
