DESCRIPTION:Spend a restorative day in Inverness exploring the art of natu
 ral inks and handmade books. We’ll begin by painting botanical inks on f
 ine papers—using organic pigments and creative mark-making techniques—
 then transform those pages into folded book forms tucked into beautiful ha
 ndmade covers.\n\nEach participant will take home a finished book and a pa
 cket of inks and papers\, along with instructions to continue creating at 
 home.\n\nThis intimate workshop will be held at Kate's House in Inverness
  and includes all materials. Please bring a lunch to share and enjoy a cr
 eative\, communal afternoon by the coast.
