 – 9 at Hanna Center’s Recreation Center\, is an exciting clinic design
 ed for serious 6th–9th grade athletes \\(ages 12 – 15\\) ready to acce
 lerate their technical skills\, tactical understanding\, and competitive c
 onfidence. From 9:00 AM to 12:00 PM\, campers will train with elite coach 
 Felipe Monroy in focused sessions covering advanced groundstrokes\, serve
