DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260409T013000
UID:260125RW2LUjBFpkGye1-5UYAIoA
DESCRIPTION:Wednesday nights at Barrel Proof Lounge just got louder\, sexi
 er\, and way more fun.\n\nKaraoke moves to the main showroom big stage eve
 ry Wednesday at 9pm\, following Open Mic\, and runs until late. Hosting th
 e night is KJ Danny D (Danny Duclos)—one of the most popular and in-dema
 nd karaoke hosts around. We’re genuinely stoked to have him bringing his
  style\, energy\, and crowd-moving presence to Downtown Santa Rosa.\n\nThi
 s isn’t sleepy bar karaoke. Danny brings a fresh\, high-energy approach 
 that turns singing into a full-on late-night experience. Big stage\, great
  sound\, packed room\, and the kind of momentum that keeps people singing 
 well past closing time.\n\nMain showroom  Starts 9pm (after Open Mic)  N
 o cover  Downtown Santa Rosa\n\nCheck out **www.barrelprooflounge.com**
  for all sorts of good times ahead.
