DESCRIPTION:Documentary Film and Performance. Join us in celebration for a
  screening of Skin to Skin\, followed by a conversation with John Santos i
 n honor of the power of music and inclusion. SANTOS–Skin to Skin is a fi
 lm portrait of community activist and seven-time Grammy nominee **John Sa
 ntos**\, a “keeper of the Afro-Caribbean flame.” Rich in musical perfo
 rmances\, Santos links the rhythms of his ancestors to contemporary strugg
 les of identity and social justice. A discussion with filmmaker Kathryn Go
 lden and a live performance with the John Santos Quartet will directly fol
 low the screening.
LOCATION:Jarvis Conservatory
