DESCRIPTION:Explore the blurred lines between everyday objects and artisti
 c expression with a focus on fiber and textile art. In this rebellion agai
 nst the distinction between Craft and Art\, we invite you to experience th
 e surprising and delightful diversity of these works while marveling at th
 e skill\, intuition\, knowledge and wisdom behind their making. The fiber 
 artists include Britt-Marie Alm\, Stephanie Brown\, Risa Iwasaki Culbertso
 n\, Amanda Farrell\, Jennifer Laursen\, Youngmi Angela Pak\, Leigh Ann Par
 ente and Vida Vazquez who each create\, in unique ways\, something new fro
 m raw or recycled materials\, intuitively and humanely imbuing them with b
 eauty and authenticity.
