UID:260106TXI_nWb07UO8KsyESTDDhQ
DESCRIPTION:Indie After Dark – Vallejo’s Night for Original Music\n\nS
 eptember 12 performers:\n\n🔥 Agness Twin\n\nSan Francisco’s hypnotic 
 post-punk / indie project led by Elisa Ovrahim. Gorgeous layered vocals\, 
 ringing guitars\, cinematic folk shadows\, and minimalist ethereal pop. Th
 eir new album Turn To Gold \\(2024\\) was mastered by John Golden \\(Sound
 garden\, Melvins\\) and has already carved its place on indie radio. Fresh
  from the Love & Rockets tour\, Agness Twin’s live set will swallow you 
 whole.\n\n🔥 Pro-Pain!\n\nBay Area 4-piece that’s “HAVING A BLAST.
 ” High-voltage energy\, pure grit\, and a sound built to light up the ro
 om. With their recent Bombs Away video\, they’re proof that Vallejo’s 
 underground scene is very much alive and screaming.\n\nEvery Second Friday
 \, Indie After Dark brings the spotlight to independent music at the intim
 ate and vibey 4th Corner Speakeasy in downtown Vallejo. Just steps from th
 e heart of the Vallejo Art Walk\, this monthly series invites you to disco
 ver bold new sounds in a setting made for connection—where the lights ar
 e low\, the cocktails are strong\, and the music runs deep.\n\nCome early 
 for the art\, stay late for the music. It’s a night where Vallejo’s cr
 eative soul shines.
LOCATION:4th Corner Speakeasy
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/indie-after-dark/164484
 46/2026-04-10T19
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
