UID:26031936ETRuGHfEWvLDomTZPdkg
DESCRIPTION:Ready to step up your salsa game? Salsa – partner dancing cl
 ass build on the basics\, introducing exciting new turns\, footwork\, and 
 partner patterns to elevate your dancing.\n\nMust have intermediate steps 
 in place\n\nProficiency in lead/follow & turns\n\nProficiency in timing & 
 partnership\n\nNo partner necessary\n\nThis class is designed for dancers 
 who have a solid foundation in salsa fundamentals and are ready to take th
 eir skills to the social dance floor. Moving beyond basic steps and patter
 ns\, we’ll focus on the essential techniques\, musicality\, and partner-
 work dynamics that make for confident and enjoyable social dancing. Drop-i
 n fee is $20 and no partner is required.\n\nDate & Time: Fridays @ 7:30PM 
 – 8:30PM\n\nAddress: 4140 Redwood Highway \\#8 San Rafael\, CA\n\nNote: 
 Arrive 10 minutes before. No floor marking shoe soles allowed.
