BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Intermediate Salsa with Tyler
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260410T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260410T193000
UID:260319QrdYUu24M06PfTpIInWw3A
DESCRIPTION:Ready to learn intermediate steps and technique?\n\nAre you a 
 salsa dancer who has the basics down but is ready to add more? Our Interme
 diate Salsa Class with Tyler is designed to help you transform your dancin
 g moves. In this class\, you’ll go beyond the basics to learn intricate 
 footwork\, enhance your leading and following skills\, and master the body
  movement that will make you shine on the dance floor. This class is for a
 nyone ready to learn the techniques and intermediate steps needed to take 
 their dancing to the next level.\n\nYou’ll learn intermediate dancing te
 chniques that will help you:\n\nExpress yourself with sharper footwork and
  styling.\n\nMaster complex turn patterns and combinations.\n\nStrengthen 
 your lead and follow for seamless\, connected dancing.\n\nAdapt to differe
 nt partners and music with ease on the social dance floor.\n\nWhat to Expe
 ct: Instructor Tyler blends a fun\, supportive atmosphere with structured
  lessons\, so you’re always challenged but never overwhelmed. Helping yo
 u progress steadily while keeping the joy of salsa front and center.\n\nDe
