 ier Andrea Immer Robinson. You will get to be part of a live studio audien
 ce through a guided tasting with special guests from the culinary and wine
  industries who will join along the way. Each event invites you to learn 
 and connect through exceptional wines\, thoughtful pairings\, and lively c
 onversation. \n\nCabernet lovers\, this one is for you. We welcome you 
 to be part of CIA at Copia’s newest wine tasting experience with Maste
 r Sommelier Andrea Immer Robinson in her *Quench at Copia* series\, wi
 th special guests and winemaking minds behind Heitz Cellar\, Brittany Sher
 wood and Master Sommelier Erik Elliot. In this experience\, you’ll be
  focusing on one of the “GOAT”-ed Grapes: Cabernet. Through a g
 uided tasting and expert insight\, you’ll uncover what gives Cabernet 
 its power\, elegance\, and unmistakable character.\n\n**This experience wi
 ll also be paired with a “Taste of The Grove” – a sample of a dish
  from The Grove Restaurant curated by our former CIA student and Miche
 lin-starred chef.**
