SUMMARY:The Brandlin Estate Wine & Food Tasting Experience
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260416T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260416T160000
UID:260312ebQRh00opU-LVs97aSdfZg
DESCRIPTION:Born on the rugged slopes of Mount Veeder\, Brandlin Estate pr
 oduces wines of structure\, intensity\, and place. The Brandlin Experience
  offers an in-depth exploration of this historic vineyard site through a c
 urated tasting of five estate-grown wines—including Zinfandel from centu
 ry-old vines and the estate’s signature Cabernet Sauvignon. This seated\
 , guided experience invites guests to delve into the mountain terroir thro
 ugh the lens of small-lot winemaking. Each wine reflects the elevation\, e
 xposure\, and rocky soils that define the Brandlin Estate. For an added di
 mension\, guests may opt to include seasonal bites\, thoughtfully paired t
 o complement the structure and complexity of the wines. This experience is
  hosted at the picturesque Boathouse.
LOCATION:Brandlin Estate 
URL:https://www.exploretock.com/brandlinestate/experience/565565/the-brand
 lin-wine-food-tasting-experience?date=2026-03-12&size=2&time=10%3A00
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
