 ir supplies if they own them. Please be on time and ready to play. Session
 s are about 30-45 minutes. Please register for this program so we have an 
 estimate for group sizes and so that we can email notifications about this
  program. ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ Looking for DMs! Are you a 13-18 and
  interested in running a game for tweens and teens? Email us at kdargeou@s
