 eventh Annual Discover Coombsville Grand Tasting Event.   More than 25 e
 steemed producers will be on hand pouring Coombsville diverse range of win
 es. Indulge in an unforgettable wine experience and join fellow wine enthu
 siasts for an elegant event featuring limited-production wines\, acclaimed
