DESCRIPTION:Join Lynmar Estate for the ultimate luxury wine and food exper
 ience in the magical setting of Quail Hill Vineyard. Enjoy an elevated\, m
 ulti-course lunch seasonally paired with ultra-premium Pinot Noir and Char
 donnay. During your meal\, Estate Chef David Frakes will make a special ta
 bleside visit to complete your experience.\n\nReservations are required. M
 aximum group size is six guests. View a sample menu here:\n\nhttps://lynma
 restate.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Collectors-Lunch-Oct-2025.pdf
