UID:260206WESCfsSy6E-MlWlCIIrM3Q
DESCRIPTION:Where unforgettable wines\, live music\, and good vibes come t
 ogether.\n\nJoin us every Saturday from 3–6 PM at Spicy Vines for a tast
 ing room experience like no other — where top local musicians from acros
 s the Bay Area meet our award-winning small-lot wines. From Rock & Roll an
 d Blues to Jazz\, Bluegrass\, and Americana\, each weekend brings new soun
 ds and new reasons to raise a glass. \n\nJenerator Jenerator is a Northe
 rn California jam band duo blending rock\, funk\, blues\, and soul into po
 werful live performances full of heart\, rhythm\, and groove. \n\nDetails
 \n\nNo cover. Walk-ins are welcome\, but this event tends to fill up quick
 ly\, so we recommend making a reservation. We are dog and family friendly!
