DESCRIPTION:Element Water: Partnership ReadingsA Tarot &amp\; Intuition Cl
 ass on Love\, Connection &amp\; Emotional Wisdom\n\n Class OverviewIn this
  immersive Water Element class\, we journey into the emotional and intuiti
 ve realms of tarot to explore relationships\, connection\, and the sacred 
 mirror of partnership.\n\nWater teaches us how to feel\, receive\, and flo
 w. Through tarot\, we will learn how to interpret the energetic exchange b
 etween two people\, uncover emotional truths\, and hold space for healing\
 , compassion\, and clarity within relationships.\n\nExperiential Elements&
 bull\; Guided meditation to connect with Water energy&bull\; Intuitive exe
 rcises to strengthen emotional reading skills&bull\; Partner practice read
 ings&bull\; Group discussion and interpretation practice\n\nTarot FocusWe 
 will work deeply with:\n\nThe Suit of Cups \\(emotions\, love\, intuition\
 \)Court Cards as relationship archetypesMajor Arcana tied to partnership \
 \(Lovers\, Devil\, Two of Cups\, etc.\\)Reversals and emotional blocks \n\
 nEnergetic IntentionThis class is a space of compassion\, emotional safety
 \, and intuitive depth.We honor that partnership readings can be tender\, 
 and we approach them with integrity\, consent\, and heart-centered awarene
 ss.
LOCATION:Songbird Community Healing Center
URL:https://mynorthbaytickets.ticketsauce.com/e/tea-and-tarot-element-wate
 r-partnerships?aff=cityspark
