DESCRIPTION:Whose ready to be a part of an amazing group of girls and yout
 h who are open minded and hearted—ready to make new friends AND develop 
 essential life skills to help them learn to live well?\n\nWe are now enrol
 ling for our School Year Wellness Workshops for girls in 3rd-8th grades.\n
 \nMeeting for a full 15 weeks\, members make fantastic friendships\, have 
 fun engaging in activities and art projects\, and learn social-emotional-p
 hysical tools that will help them throughout their lifetime.\n\nWe’ve go
 t 3 amazing facilitators and workshops are hosted at McKinley School in Pe
 taluma-though members come from a variety of schools and towns to attend o
 pening up even further opportunities for making even more friends!\n\n\\*G
 rades 3/4 meets on Wednesday's from Jan 14-May 13\n\n\\*Grades 5/6 meets o
 n Tuesday's Jan 13-May 12\n\n\\*Additional Grades 5/6 meets on Wednesdays 
 from Jan 14-May 13\n\n\\*Grades 7/8 meets on Thursday's from Jan 15-May 14
 \n\nReady to learn more and register?\n\nwisegirlworkshops.com/workshops-a
 nd-services/school-year-wellness-workshop-series/\n\nHere’s to growing W
 ise Girls and Youth!
LOCATION:McKinley School
URL:https://bohemian.com/events-calendar/#/details/wise-girl-workshops-sch
 ool-year-wellness-workshops/17774459/2026-04-22T16
X-SOURCE:North Bay Bohemian
END:VEVENT
